# K8s Manifests Conventions

## CloudNativePG Cluster

```yaml
apiVersion: postgresql.cnpg.io/v1
kind: Cluster
metadata:
  name: pg-{app}
  namespace: puchi-db
spec:
  instances: 1
  imageName: ghcr.io/cloudnative-pg/postgresql:18.0
  storage:
    size: 10Gi
    storageClass: local-path
  bootstrap:
    initdb:
      database: {db_name}
      owner: {username}
      secret:
        name: pg-{app}-secret
```

## Garage buckets

Tạo bucket qua Garage v2 admin API:

```bash
curl -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"globalAlias":"puchi-{bucket}"}' \
  http://{garage}:3903/v2/CreateBucket
```

## NATS streams

Tạo stream với subject prefix `puchi.*`:

```bash
nats str add puchi-{name} \
  --subjects "puchi.{domain}.>" \
  --storage file \
  --max-bytes=1GB
```

## Labels

- Tất cả resource gán label `app: puchi`
- Namespace pattern: `puchi-{env}` (puchi-db, puchi-infra, puchi-app)
